Subject: [PATCH] RDMA/core: Prevent divide-by-zero error triggered by the user
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.12.7
Git-commit: 54d87913f147a983589923c7f651f97de9af5be1

[ Upstream commit 54d87913f147a983589923c7f651f97de9af5be1 ]

